Class TaxonomyNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mpa.analysis.taxonomy.TaxonomyNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable

    public class TaxonomyNode
extends Object
implements Comparable, Serializable
    This class represents a NCBI taxonomy entry, complete with taxonomy ID as well as rank and name specifiers.

    R. Heyer and A. Behne
